name: Bukit Bulgari
address: GG6X+42R, Ngis, Manggis, Karangasem Regency, Bali 80871, Indonesia
review 1:
The view across the valley and bay is nice. One can see the rice fields and the ships running into the harbor in the distance.
The hike up here from the main road is along a paved road with a few quite steep sections - prepare to sweat and take it slow on the way down - might be slippery.
At the time of writing, the roads in gmap do not match the environment.
